OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMarvel Comics 'legend' John
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FRomita Sr dies             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Marvel Comics artist John Romita Sr,   
OL,6, who helped to create characters such as
OL,7, Wolverine and Spider-Man's girlfriend  
OL,8, Mary Jane Watson, has died aged 93.    
OL,10,FHe also had a hand in other favourites 
OL,11,Fsuch as Kingpin and the Punisher.      
OL,13,FHis death was confirmed on Tuesday by  
OL,14,Fhis son and fellow comics artist John  
OL,15,FRomita Jr, who confirmed his father had
OL,16,F"passed away peacefully in his sleep". 
OL,18,F"He is a legend in the art world and it
OL,19,Fwould be my honour to follow in his    
OL,20,Ffootsteps," he posted on social media. 
